44
45/// Request to create Cell in MAC and Scheduler.
46/// \remark See O-RAN WG8, Section 9.2.1.1.
47struct mac_cell_creation_request {
48 du_cell_index_t cell_index;
49 pci_t pci;
50
51 /// subcarrierSpacing for common, used for initial access and broadcast message.
52 subcarrier_spacing scs_common;
53
54 carrier_configuration dl_carrier;
55 carrier_configuration ul_carrier;
56 ssb_configuration ssb_cfg;
57
58 /// Embedded scheduler cell configuration request.
59 sched_cell_configuration_request_message sched_req;
60
61 bool cell_barred;
62 bool intra_freq_resel;
63
64 /// BCCH-DL-SCH Message payload containing the SIB1 and SI messages to be broadcast.
65 std::vector<byte_buffer> bcch_dl_sch_payloads;
66
67 // TODO: Fill remaining fields
68};
69
70} // namespace srsran
